N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 5-2.10 - Certificate or letter of compliance

State Regulations

Upon satisfactory completion of the requirements of the permit issuing official as contained in sections 5-2.9 and
5-2.13
of this Subpart, a certificate of compliance will be issued to the applicant. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10
§§
5-2.10

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
